                  <paragraph>Bottles of 12 ...................................NDC  43386-140-12</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Bottles of 28....................................NDC  43386-140-28</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Bottles of 100 ................................NDC  43386-140-01</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">STORE AND DISPENSE</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Tablets: Store below 25°C (77°F); in tight, light-resistant container.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Manufactured by:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Novel Laboratories, Inc.</paragraph>
